reviewText: A very good, well rounded answer to the question "who the fcuk is Billy Childish". Buy it or rent it if you like punk, blues, garage or rock n roll. He's a living legend and you should know who he is by now.

An excellent documentary.

Brilliant all round really....a big insight into the man...good music scenes, good candid scenes, interesting & informative.

It's a shame he's dead

;-)
